She walked onto the bridge and saw Kluster.  "Hello there.  Need any 
help with anything?" She looked down for a second and saw her 
predacon symbol on her shoulder. She looked back up at Kluster. "Or 
better yet, got a better looking symbol I could use?" She gave him a 
warm, friendly smile.
